*Svetlost* je bitna za život na Zemlji. (Light is essential for life on Earth.)

U *svetlosti* njegovih očiju osvetlio se celi svet. (In the *light* of his eyes, the whole world was illuminated.)

Mnogi ljudi se izgube u *svetlosti* slavnih dana. (Many people get lost in the *glory* of famous days.)

On je kročio u *svetlost* slave. (He stepped into the *glory* of fame.)

Kao *svetlost* u tami, ona je svetla tačka u našim životima. (Like a *light* in the darkness, she is a bright spot in our lives.)